net.minecraftforge.fml.event.lifecycle

类 FMLDedicatedServerSetupEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
      • net.minecraftforge.fml.event.lifecycle.ModLifecycleEvent
        • net.minecraftforge.fml.event.lifecycle.FMLDedicatedServerSetupEvent

  • public class FMLDedicatedServerSetupEvent
extends ModLifecycleEvent
    This is the second of four commonly called events during mod lifecycle startup. Called before InterModEnqueueEvent Called after FMLCommonSetupEvent Called on net.minecraftforge.api.distmarker.Dist#DEDICATED_SERVER - the dedicated game server. Alternative to FMLClientSetupEvent. Do dedicated server specific activities with this event. This is a parallel dispatch event.
